flutter_mobx.description: Flutter integration for MobX. It provides a set of Observer widgets that automatically rebuild when the tracked observables change.

mobx.description: MobX is a library for reactively managing the state of your applications. Use the power of observables, actions, and reactions to supercharge your Dart and Flutter apps.

mobx_codegen.description: Code generator for MobX that adds support for annotating your code with @observable, @computed, @action and also creating Store classes.
